# Figure artwork. A local working area for the image pipeline (scrape -> cutout
# -> upload:catalog), not part of the app: the app reads figure images only from
# Supabase, and ships none of its own. Deliberately not committed - Supabase is
# the source of truth for this art, and 25MB of PNGs in the bundle is what this
# replaced. See scripts/upload-catalog-images.mjs.
catalog-images/
